\ip God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Nahum, e derav…®ram an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®fozir puvat…®. Niniven nguibar ekiam a ikuvigha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ak…®nafarir an osirizir kam, kar an m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar akongeziba. 
\ip Ninive, a kantri Asirian nguibar ekiam. Asiria a kantrin bar gavgavir mam, ez…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba kantrin igharazir av…®ribar gumazamizibav sogha me ab…®ni. Kantrin kamra not…®n amadaghan Israelian kantri gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha an gumazamiziba inigha ghuez…®, me danganir igharazibar iti. 
\ip Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia orazi apaniba Niniven nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ghiz…®, me bar akonge. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Nahum kamagh…®n m…®gei, me akaba batogha arazir kurar av…®rim gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God men arazir kuraba ikarvagha uab…® bizir kam gamiz…®, a Ninive bato. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Niniven nguibar ekiam gas…®ghas…®ki 
