\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Onger Akaba 25:8; 28:8; 37:39-40\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an arazir aghuibar e gami. 
\q2 Os…®mt…®zibar dughiabar a uan gumazamizibar mogomer danganim…®n m…®n ikia, 
